<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهُوَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- فِي الحَبِّ اشْتِدَادُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَفِي الثَّمَرِ بُدُوُّ صَلَاحِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَلَا يَسْتَقِرُّ إِلَّا بِجَعْلِهَا فِي بَيْدَرٍ وَنَحْوِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَجِبُ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> العُشْرُ فِيمَا سُقِيَ بِلَا كُلْفَةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَنِصْفُهُ فِيمَا سُقِيَ بِهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَثَلَاثَةُ أَرْبَاعِهِ فِيمَا سُقِيَ بِهِمَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> فَإِنْ تَفَاوَتَا: اعْتُبِرَ الأَكْثَرُ نَفْعًا وَنُمُوًّا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَمَعَ الجَهْلِ العُشْرُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَيَجْتَمِعُ عُشْرٌ وَخَرَاجٌ فِي أَرْضٍ خَرَاجِيَّةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span> مَا فُتِحَتْ عَنْوةً وَلَمْ تُقْسَمُ بَيْنَ الغَانِمِينَ -غَيْرَ مَكَّةَ -؛ كَمِصْرَ وَالشَّامِ وَالعِرَاقِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَفِي العَسَلِ العُشْرُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> سَوَاءٌ أَخَذَهُ مِنْ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- مَوَاتٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- أَوْ مَمْلُوكَةٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>